beer.beer_description: She may look like your mum on a big night out but the Matriarch is much more than meets the eye: a sheep dressed up in lambs clothing’ slightly hazy and all foam on top. The juiciest rumours surround her life but they pale in comparison to the truth. She lives her life in the fast lane; tropical destinations and flavours abound.  Citrus, pineapple, stone fruit coat the mouth and overcome the senses. She's generous with her perfume like this brew is with aromas of citrus, pineapple and stone fruit. Her delivery is always fresh. She should be bitter from all she’s seen and done (and the crazy amount of hops used) but instead she is a fresh, hopped up juicy number that's full bodied in every sense of the word.

items.badge_description: Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 475 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 96!

At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 20 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 5!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 270 different IPAs.  Try 5 more for Level 55!
